headline: Swisscard Partnership Expansion Could Be a Game Changer for Fair Isaac (FICO)
summary: Swisscard recently announced it has extended its partnership with FICO to optimize credit limit strategies for both new and existing cardholders, utilizing the FICO Platform’s advanced analytics to allow for increased flexibility while managing risk. This move positions Swisscard as a first mover in the market, aiming to improve customer satisfaction and loyalty by adopting more tailored credit management approaches.
